Hello all, I'm starting work on https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/80658

It's been a bit since I dove into the Compiler internals. While I can find the related test fairly easily, could someone point me to where in the non-test code I would want to start to fix this?

And it looks like this file in the current code base is the one that needs to be changed https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/db69136369bc2baf3c2244b57e6541dc558d0f2c/compiler/rustc_infer/src/infer/error_reporting/mod.rs
Made decent progress on it this afternoon, will continue when able this week
